<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="29" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="29">Distribution and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="29">
Endemic to Ecuador (provinces of 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bolívar">Bolivar</normalizedToken>
and Chimborazo) (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Distribution map of Xenophyllum funkianum (left hand) and X. lorochaqui (right hand)." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.139.47872.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/375446" pageId="0" pageNumber="29">3</figureCitation>
). It grows in exposed places and sandy soils of the dry superparamo, at elevations of 4100-4300 m.
</paragraph>
